message.text:
Hi tams! Anyone interested in applying in call center (Alorica)? I will help you pass the application process.

- Student friendly (accepting students)
- Competitive salary (18k - 24k)
- Considerate Trainers & TMs
- Has a lot of incentives 
- 20% night differential 
- Rice & meal allowance 
- Graveyard shift
-500-1k upon reaching final interview
- 1k - 2k eGift if you pass the application process

Available Sites:

Alorica Sta. Mesa
Alorica Cubao

Qualification:

- Senior high graduate

Pm po for more info and if interested
